Documentary that brings pioneering images that capture the dazzling array of mysterious and wonderful creatures that live in China&#039;s most beautiful landscapes. The vast Tibetan plateau is one of the world&#039;s most remote places and home to chiruantelopes, wild yaks, foxes and bears.
